---

<AcademyLayout title={title} description={description} locale={locale} activeNav="90-day-map">
  <main class="edu-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>90-Day Map</h1>
      <p>30-60-90 day action map — goals, milestones, roadmap.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="content-placeholder">
      <p>Content under construction per Master Plan V2 — Sprint 1 route skeleton.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</AcademyLayout>
